metadata.name: apegoblin #1
metadata.description: Once upon a time, in a dense jungle far away, a group of bored apes were tired of their mundane lives. They had explored every inch of their jungle and had nothing left to discover. One day, they stumbled upon a mysterious potion called 'Apedust'. The label on the bottle read, 'Warning: Consume at your own risk.' But the curious apes decided to drink it anyway. As soon as they consumed the potion, a strange energy coursed through their bodies. Their limbs elongated, their teeth sharpened, and their skin turned a sickly green color. They had mutated into goblins!
